              "taskListText": "1. Prove successful checkout end to end\n2. Confirm subscription activation unlocks the account\n3. Handle failed payments cleanly\n4. Verify cancellation through the Stripe customer portal\n5. Confirm webhook handling and duplicate-event safety\n6. Confirm receipt email expectations\n7. Verify account state after renewal\n8. Verify account state after expiration\n9. Define upgrade and downgrade behavior\n10. Define refund handling",
              "questionListText": "1. Do we need more than one paid plan at beta?",
